# Bitaxe Monitor Bot

A Telegram-based monitoring system for Bitaxe Bitcoin miners using an ESP32.

## Features
- Real-time monitoring of hashrate, temperature, and bestDiff.
- Automated reports every 6 hours.
- Alerts for high temp (>65Â°C) and low hashrate (<100 GH/s) with auto-restart.
- 7-day statistics with ASCII bars.

## Setup
1. Clone this repo.
2. Create `config.h` with your Wi-Fi, Telegram, and Bitaxe IPs (see template in code comments).
3. Install libraries: `ArduinoJson`, `UniversalTelegramBot`.
4. Upload to ESP32.

## Usage
- `/start`: Begin monitoring.
- `/report`: Get a detailed report.
- `/stats`: View 7-day stats.

Full documentation in progress.
